column5: I happened to "Google Images" "Huge Muskie"  I came across this picture a few years ago , I darn near fell out of my chair ... I couldn't remember catching this fish ... I showed it to all my family and lifelong friends just a few realized it wasn't me... I put this up as my "facebook" profile picture... I've had tons of compliments on "my" catch... I've always fessed up and NEVER claimed that I caught it.  Whaddaya think?  Me   Not me.   Me   Not me  Me   Me  Randy
Whoa......looks like it's gonna be a long "winternet" this year
Your non bologcal twin catches better fish than you
Randy, You're a far better looking specimen than your look a like IMHO anyway
because wearing a baseball cap, sunglasses, and sporting a goatee makes you a rare specimen
Randy, You should hire a P.I. to track him down. Send him to work for you so you can google images all day.
Sure as hell cut from the same cloth; that's for sure!
i found this guy looks EXACTLY like me....    uncanny!
I think it looks like you Randy!
